Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.build.AbstractBuildable

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class Item
extends AbstractConfigurable
    The base portion of a Counter Layout component. Contains the draw() method, but may override specific values from an associated (via the name attribute) ItemInstance
